properties.areaDesc: Coastal waters from Chincoteague to Parramore Island VA out 20 nm; Coastal waters from Parramore Island to Cape Charles Light VA out 20 nm
properties.headline: Low Water Advisory issued February 9 at 12:52AM EST until February 9 at 2:00AM EST by NWS Wakefield VA
properties.description:
* WHAT...Abnormally low water levels.

* WHERE...Coastal waters from Chincoteague to Parramore Island
VA out 20 nm and Coastal waters from Parramore Island to Cape
Charles Light VA out 20 nm.

* WHEN...Until 2 AM EST early this morning.

* IMPACTS...Below normal water levels will result in hazardous
navigating conditions.
properties.instruction:
Mariners should navigate shallow waters with extreme caution due
to below normal water levels.

NWSheadline: LOW WATER ADVISORY IN EFFECT UNTIL 2 AM EST EARLY THIS MORNING
